				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Yes, simply splicing the cables will work. It'll be hard to make it look good, though. Also, they changed the colors of the wires inside the cables, so it won't just be brown-&gt;brown.<br /><br />Reportedly, most 1- or 2-player games for the Famicom treat players 3 and 4 as duplicates of players 1 and 2, so an ordinary Famicom 4-player adapter should work, too.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

